{"tid":2139946,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"青衣區中學遭掟汽油彈刑毀4人被捕 警方不排除有人透過破壞學校希望校方能夠罷課","createTime":"2020-08-04T15:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T06:28:37.000Z","uid":50386,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"af614a06482725a9b90bd5bf9883515829959441","tid":2139946,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T15:29:10.000Z","msg":"青衣長康邨樂善堂梁植偉紀念中學於5月25日及7月24日分別被人用伸縮警棍及投擲汽油彈破壞學校正門，警方經調查後拘捕3名男子，涉嫌縱火、刑事毁壞及藏有攻擊性武器等，其中一人為該校的畢業生，另外兩人則為仍在該校就讀的學生。<br />\n<br />\n葵青警區助理指揮官(刑事)林志源警司指，被捕的其中兩名男子於7月25日當天，先將石油氣罐放在學校正門，然後再將裝有白電油的玻璃樽點燃並掟向校門，引起爆炸，經調查後，<span class=\"red\">不排除有人希望校方能夠罷課，透過破壞學校而阻止其他學生上課</span>，又指會繼續調查，不排除有更多人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200804/GRIZ3VBBLV6WPQRKCRFDRDH6A4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200804%2FGRIZ3VBBLV6WPQRKCRFDRDH6A4%2F&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd08L9AbO9EvXEPTzVQ1jYSs%3D&h=8681f3f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200804%2FGRIZ3VBBLV6WPQRKCRFDRDH6A4%2F&h=54d1d52d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200804/GRIZ3VBBLV6WPQRKCRFDRDH6A4/</a><br />\n<br />\n7月25號一早停咗課啦<br />\n又放緊暑假<br />\n罷乜嘢課呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee3bb4454de274e29f4f999aa4b4bcc8fac2cb57","tid":2139946,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T15:29:34.000Z","msg":"連登熱門做乜撚嘢？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2139924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2139924</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"725f6df4e710c4c97eed07003239d15ac23e71c9","tid":2139946,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T15:32:36.000Z","msg":"校方點罷課<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/bi